Css:
-----------
1. by using id: #<id value>
2. by using class: .<class value>
3. by attributes: tagName[attributeName='attribute value']
4. by tagname: tagname
5. tag + id: format: tagname#id_value [example: input#email]
6. tag + className: tagname.<class_value>
7. multiple attribute: textarea[name='bio'][placeholder='Tell us about yourself']
8. parent > child: #loginForm > button
9. start-with: div[id^='loginAlert']
10. ends-with: div[id$='loginAlert']
11. contains: div[id*='loginAlert']